      "seed": 1266799648,
      "version": 858,
      "versionNonce": 976342511,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774558847252,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FR:\nuser should be able to:\n- upload a file to KB\n- ask questions and get answers based on KB only\n- answers should include  quoute of sourses\n- see a KB backoffice dashboard where we see:\n    - processing stats about the KB\n    - the actual clean documents\n\n\nnon-FR:\n- for upload file:\n    - accuracy > latency \n- for ask:\n    - accuracy > latency \n\n\nout of scope:\n- fallback to general knowledge if no relevant info in kb\n- cleaning/preprocessing - the UI receives clean md files\n- auth",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FR:\nuser should be able to:\n- upload a file to KB\n- ask questions and get answers based on KB only\n- answers should include  quoute of sourses\n- see a KB backoffice dashboard where we see:\n    - processing stats about the KB\n    - the actual clean documents\n\n\nnon-FR:\n- for upload file:\n    - accuracy > latency \n- for ask:\n    - accuracy > latency \n\n\nout of scope:\n- fallback to general knowledge if no relevant info in kb\n- cleaning/preprocessing - the UI receives clean md files\n- auth",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PzGZTAmasa3kVfXHe-YF5",
